00:37:52.520 --> 00:37:54.055
I think you referenced--

00:37:54.055 --> 00:37:55.013
LEONARD MLODINOW: Nash.

00:37:55.013 --> 00:37:56.480
SPEAKER: Yeah, John Nash.

00:37:56.480 --> 00:37:58.480
LEONARD MLODINOW: He was
