00:38:04.220 --> 00:38:07.180
got him the Nobel Prize, and
then he went over the edge

00:38:07.180 --> 00:38:10.810
and he schizophrenic for some
years, and then he recovered.

00:38:10.810 --> 00:38:11.720
SPEAKER: Yeah.

00:38:11.720 --> 00:38:13.090
We have another question.

00:38:13.090 --> 00:38:17.270
AUDIENCE: Yeah, so I'm
actually an improviser as well

00:38:17.270 --> 00:38:18.590
as somebody here.

00:38:18.590 --> 00:38:21.890
And so it seems to
