00:43:37.230 --> 00:43:39.100
with what I was
talking about failure

00:43:39.100 --> 00:43:46.090
and about how sometimes the
best elastic thinking comes

00:43:46.090 --> 00:43:48.622
from when you don't
accept what you see,

00:43:48.622 --> 00:43:51.080
or when you don't accept that
you're not going to get there

00:43:51.080 --> 00:43:52.580
and you just keep trying.

00:43:52.580 --> 00:43:55.760
So the idea is that if you
broaden your perspective

00:43:55.760 --> 00:43:59.350
and the amount that--

00:43:59.350 --> 00:44:03.295
broaden the range of ideas that
you find that you'll consider

00:44:03.295 --> 00:44:05.230
or that your brain
proposes to you,

00:44:05.230 --> 00:44:07.410
you have a much greater
chance of solving a problem,

00:44:07.410 --> 00:44:10.900
even though you think that
it can't possibly be solved.

